🖤Inspiration Photos 

Having a Reference photo of what you want to achieve, really helps us narrow down a perfect consultation. 

My advice: Bring 3photos of what you Love and 3 photos of what you Hate. This will give us a range of where to go and where to stay away from.

In the end we’re all Happy to help find photos. Bringing some just gives us a lil more time to Create.

Xo
Ernesto 

#sfhair #sfsalon #sfstylist #hairstyles #longhair #shorthairideas #longhairideas #menshair

🖤BeeHive Layer 

I always think of a Beehive when creating this full vintage shape. 

So I decided to name it that.

It adds shorter layers at crown for height and gradually increases in length to front of face. If you pull it back in a ponytail the crown stays disconnected to add lift . 

I couldn’t keep it looking too styled , so I roughed it up with a salt spray.

🖤Jared

GreyBlend 
And a Haircut.

Jared was getting married and I recommended dying his beard for the occasion.  Let’s face it.  His Beard will always be grey ,that’s a fact. 

Why not play with it. 

Grey one month dark the next.  His now wife was thrilled and now he has options.

#sf #greyhair #greyblending #beard #greybeard #sfhair #sfstylist

🖤Textured Shag 

Cut w/ Shears Only 

Smoothed out for weight removal. 
Dry cutting has always helped me create shapes within shapes, creating more flow and extending the length of time between cuts. 

The hair is best Naturally air dried with styling products. 
I love adding  styling textures to give more punches up results. 

Play with your Hair

🖤Signature Cut

For quite some time now, I’ve been refining my craft. 

The concept of having a signature cut used to intimidate me, as I feared I’d be confined to a single style. However, my perspective has evolved. I now view it as a finely-honed skill cherished by clients who appreciate my artistic vision.

Today in class, hearing people say, “I know it’s Ernesto’s work just by looking at it” .made me blush. 

Thank you @nicolecudzilo for allowing me to create a special shape with its own details to complement her personality. 

can’t wait to see what’s next
